NAME: Name [text]
LABEL: Name
DESCRIPTION: Titles, identifying phrases, or names given to an archaeological space.

NAME: Project Associator
LABEL: KORA identifier for the Project record that describes the overarching archaeological enterprise when this field research season or campaign took place.

NAME: Title
LABEL: Title given to a particular physical configuration of the named project in an officially-defined short span of time

NAME: Type
LABEL: Particular type of season (e.g. session, excavation, study)

NAME: Director
LABEL: Person(s) who bear responsibility for the execution of the season

NAME: Registrar
LABEL: Person(s) in an official position responsible for accurately recording season data

NAME: Contributor
LABEL: Person(s) who participated in the project during this particular season

NAME: Contributor Role
LABEL: Part or roles played by person identified in Contributor field.

NAME: Earliest Date
LABEL: Earliest date associated with project activity in this particular season, expressed in yyyy/mm/dd format

NAME: Latest Date
LABEL: Latest date associated with project activity in this particular season, expressed in yyyy/mm/dd format

NAME: Terminus Ante Quem
LABEL: Date at which the project location studied in this season begins to exhibit evidence of human activity.

NAME: Terminus Post Quem
LABEL: Date at which the project location studied in this season ceases to exhibit evidence of human activity.

NAME: Description
LABEL: Concise narrative outlining the season, its goals, duration, outputs, etc.
